The Best Eyeliner Tutorials on Instagram I love eyeliner be it kohl, liquid, gel or cake and I love a good thirty second eyeliner tutorial showing me how I can get beautiful winged liner in the blink of an eye. Here’s ten Instagram videos of different eyeliner tutorials that you simply must see (and yes they will make you want to rush to your room and try them all for yourselves.)
1) Thin Winged Eyeliner



✨Gold and Brown✨ @miaumauve
A video posted by Makeup Tutorials & Videos  (@makeuptutorials111) on Aug 12, 2015 at 8:20am PDT


Up first is a classic winged eyeliner look with a thinner flick and I love this no fuss, straight to the point tutorial that shows us how to get our eyeliner en point as well.
2) Thick Winged Eyeliner



@loveyadearly Perfection #dramaticmakeup #dramaticeye #makeuptutorials #makeuptutorial #makeup #eyeliner #eyemakeup #eyeshadow #eyelinertutorial #eyeshadowtutorial #doubleeyeliner #perfect #perfectmakeup #pretty #cute #girl #tutorial #thickliner #blackeyeliner A video posted by Makeup Tutorials & Videos  (@makeuptutorials111) on Jun 20, 2015 at 2:52pm PDT


This may be similar to the first tutorial but don’t be fooled, not only does this show you how to do both eyes, but this is a fatter wing for those who prefer a more dramatic look.
3) Electric Blue Winged Eyeliner



▶️REPOSTING this video (for people who don’t scroll down my feed) • you don’t wanna miss this  by @cyn_xo . I’m not sure but I think she is using the NYX studio liquid liner in extreme blue 
A video posted by makeupvideos (@makeupvideos5) on Jun 29, 2015 at 11:36am PDT


I literally cannot get over how amazing this electric blue eyeliner looks, this tutorial is great for showing you how to wing it with liquid eyeliner, plus that shade of blue is absolutely gorgeous. If blue isn’t your colour switch it for a shade of Pantone for an on-trend fall look.
4) Flicked Winged Eyeliner



Eyeliner tutorial  by @iheartmakeupart ♡♡ A video posted by @make.up.holics on Sep 23, 2015 at 3:49am PDT


Yes this is another black, winged eyeliner tutorial but rather than showing you how it’s done, this particular tutorial shows us the shapes and angles to get that perfect wing which is why it’s one of our favourite videos.
5) Rainbow Winged Eyeliner



Here’s a short tutorial showing how I created my rainbow winged eyeliner look in support of gay pride and marriage equality!❤️ Products used ✨ @maccosmetics texture and orange eyeshadows in the crease @makeupforeverofficial flash colour case palette (I had to mix a few of the shades together to get the colours I wanted) with a Mac 210 brush. I used a Mac 228 brush to blend the colours together @inglotireland 76 eyeliner gel, @stilacosmetics emerald smudge stick and @maccosmetics sassy moss fluidline all in the waterline @sugarpill darling pigment and @stargazerproducts blue glitter under the eye @eylureofficial 145 lashes @anastasiabeverlyhills dipbrow in ebony #irishmua #irishmakeupartist #bblogger #gaypride #marriageequality #marref #rainbow #rainboweyeliner #voteyes #anastasiabrows #makeupforever #maccosmetics #inglot #stargazer #marriageequality #yesequality #colourful #blending #wingedliner #wingedlinertutorial #tutorial #howto #makeuptutorial #makeupbyserenacleary #slave2beauty #vegas_nay #hudabeauty #wakeupandmakeup
A video posted by ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀Serena Cleary (@makeupbyserenacleary) on May 5, 2015 at 2:02pm PDT


Who says that gay pride has to be limited to only one day? This pride inspired eyeliner is absolutely show stopping, and if you can’t pick a colour why not use all of them with this easy to follow rainbow liner tutorial?
6) Shimmery Eyes and Winged Eyeliner



A video posted by Sigma Beauty (@sigmabeauty) on Sep 18, 2015 at 8:05pm PDT


Anyone who says that one eyeliner tutorial is all you need is utterly wrong because not only does this show you how to perfect your winged liner, but it also offers a stunning shimmery look on the lids that you can replicate at home.
7) Winged Eyeliner using Tape

Kat Von D Star Studded Eyeshadow Book Is there such thing as makeup porn? Because it kind of feels like it with the Kat Von D Star Studded Eyeshadow Book ($66 CAD, exclusively at Sephora). Never have I felt so strongly for a formulation of eyeshadows together in one awesome palette. The Kat Von D Star Studded Eyeshadow Book is a palette of 24 eyeshadows in varying colours and finishes. The palette is split into ... doing my makeup while drinking coffee and have a little spill? Goodbye, pretty palette. In terms of formulation... The Good: Holy ASLKDFJSDFASF. The Kat Von D eyeshadows are some of the best I've ever tried. According to the almighty Sephora website, it's a patented, triple-milled formula, ... probably won't be interested in this palette. But if you've ever flirted with the idea of coloured eyeshadow, then the Kat Von D Star Studded Eyeshadow Book will tickle your fancy. It's got ridiculous colours and while some are not particularly wearable, others somehow manage to look quite flattering. Have you tried Kat Von D eyeshadows? mich hier ebenfalls die Farbe, da sie im OnlineShop eher nach "Pflaume" aussah. Aber ansonsten kann ich nicht meckern. ❤ Kat von D - "Lock it" Fixing Spray: Da Mein Urban Decay  Spray gerade leer ging, bot es sich an, dieses Spray mal ... ist es nicht groß besser als andere günstigere wie beispielsweise von NYX. Nice to  have, aber kein Must Have. ❤ Kat von D - "Hawkwind": Eine der neuesten Farben aus der Reihe, die mich absolut überzeugt.  Die Lippies von Kat sind mir nicht neu und bis auf den etwas zu langen Applikator (mein Empfinden) kann ich absolut nichts aussetzen. ❤ Kat von D - "Lovesick": Ebenfalls eine wunderschöne Farbe, die meines Erachtens ein Dupe zu Makeup Factorys "Velvet Mauve" ist. ❤ Kat von D - "Alchemist" Highlighter Palette: Dies ist im wahrsten Sinne des Wortes mein Highlight der Bestellung. Anfangs war ich mir unsicher ... Tag, aber dafür pink und lila umso mehr - insofern man es gerne bunt mag. COSA NON FARSI SCAPPARE AI SALDI SEPHORA 2018: EVERLASTING LIP DUO – KAT VON D
Apro il post con l’Everlasting Lip Duo di Kat Von D, che contiente due tonalità, Superbia e Melancholia, perfette per creare un bell’effetto ombré sulle labbra ma che, anche da sole, sanno essere molto belle!

Kat Von D, Everlasting Lip Duo kit contorno labbra. Prezzo in offerta: 9,50€ su Sephora.it 
La loro tenuta è molto buona, si stendono ... le labbra rimangono piacevolmente colorate, con un effetto simile a quello di una tinta labbra, che dura per diverse ore.

KAT VON D – THE BOW N ARROW LOOK DUO MINI EYELINER E MINI ROSSETTO LIQUIDO
Ecco un altro suggerimento da non farsi sfuggire con i saldi firmato Kat Von D: il duo The Bow N Arrow Look! Contiene un mini Ink Liner nel colore nero Trooper, ed un mini rossetto liquido Everlasting nella nuance Bow N Arrow, nude e matte.

Kat Von D, The Bow N Arrow Look Duo mini eyeliner e mini rossetto liquido. Prezzo in offerta: 12,50€ su Sephora.it 
L’ Ink

dubbio l’Epic Ink Eyeliner di NYX. Ovviamente, essendo quasi identici a suo parere, ama molto anche il Tattoo Liner di Kat Von D. Durante il corso del 2017 ho avuto modo di conoscere e innamorarsi del tipo di punta, con setole in nylon, ... tenere sempre di scorta!

LAURA E IL CORRETTORE DELLA VITA
Il prodotto dell’anno di Laura è il correttore Lock-it di Kat von D, che le ha permesso di abbandonare tutti i prodotti precedenti e trovare così il correttore della vita! Nonostante abbia la ... la sua opinione questo è molto superiore: rispetto al Bobbi in versione concealer è più coprente e dura di più.
Kat Von D, Lock-it concealer. Prezzo: 26€ Su Sephora.it
A volte le capita di usare un correttore secco solo in caso di brufoli

interessantissimo prodotto e vi diremo se è davvero valido come sembra! Restate sintonizzate mi raccomando! 
LOCK-IT IL FONDOTINTA COPRENTE DI KAT VON D
Ormai sapete che i prodotti di Kat Von D sono tra i preferiti miei e del mio Team! Le ragazze infatti spesso vi hanno parlato di quanto amano i suoi prodotti e il correttore della collezione Lock-It è tra i loro prodotti preferiti del 2017.

Il fondotinta di Kat Von D è davvero unico! Basta una piccolissima dose per rendere la pelle del viso omogenea, coprire tutte le imperfezioni e lasciare una delicatissima texture matt. La formula, oltre alla coprenza davvero altissima, ha una durata extra lunga!

Kat Von D, Lock-It Fondotinta Coprente. Prezzo: 34,50 € su sephora.it
